import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';

const Wrapper = styled.div`
  display: block;
  padding 24px;
`


const UserInfo = () => (
    <React.Fragment>
        <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridEmail">
                <Form.Label>Mail</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="name@example.com" />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group>
                <Form.File id="exampleFormControlFile1" label="Ladda upp bild" />
            </Form.Group>
        </Form.Row>

        <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="firstName">
                <Form.Label>First name</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="Karl" />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="lastName">
                <Form.Label>Last name</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="Jansson" />
            </Form.Group>
        </Form.Row>

        <Form.Row>
            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="title">
                <Form.Label>Titel</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="LÃ¤rare"/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="phone">
                <Form.Label>Telefon nummer</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="+46760042337"/>
            </Form.Group>
        </Form.Row>
    </React.Fragment>
)

const CvForm = () => (
  <Wrapper>
    <Form>
        <UserInfo/>
    </Form>
  </Wrapper>
)


export default CvForm
